    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MAIN FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Avatar customization</li><li>Many items that can be placed anywhere</li><li>All items can be made any size</li><li>All items can be recolored</li><li>Items can be made climbable</li><li>All items can be left frozen or made to be affected by physics</li><li> Place traps, enemies, obstacles, and much more</li><li> Import your own models</li><li> Share and try community made maps using Steam Workshop</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WHAT WILL YOU BUILD</strong></h2>Use your imagination to build Your World anyway you want. You build the landscape and everything in it. Build a giant obstacle course to try and conquer with traps, enemies, and even a boss that gains new abilities as its weakened, or anything else you could imagine. Use the npc builder to create custom made npc's from any items you choose to make a truly unique companion. All progress can be saved and shared through the Steam Workshop. Join the discord for tips , help, or to share or find community made worlds ",
